OSMM — Open Source Makerspace Manager
Copyright (C) 2026 OSMM contributors.

OSMM is a self-hostable, multi-tenant management platform built for makerspace
communities — covering inventory, tool and equipment lending, and 3D printing in
one place — so a community can see what tools and equipment exist, who borrowed
what, what is available, and how every loan and print job moves from request to
completion, without spreadsheets or guesswork.

